A highly detailed and unsettling Magic: The Gathering card art depicting a sickly, iridescent slime ooze with swirling, grotesque faces emerging from its depths, casting a sickly green glow, with a background of decaying gothic architecture, in the style of old, unsettling fairytale illustrations, dramatic lighting, magic-mana-large symbols, 2B casting cost, -1/-1 effect highlighted subtly.